<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>lái ba ràng wǒ men xiàng shén yǎng liǎn 迦南759</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 lái ba ràng wǒ men xiàng shén yǎng liǎn,
 yīn wèi tā de líng zhèng yùn xíng. zhǔ jiù zài wǒ men zhōng jiān.
 měi yī tiān de shēng huó, měi yī tiān de xíng wèi,
 dōu wán quán xiǎn míng zài zhǔ de miàn qián.
 duō shǎo de fù chū, xīn zhōng yǒu shén me yì niàn,
 fù zài àn zhōng bì tiān tiān chá kàn.
 bù yào zhǐ zài yǎn qián shì fèng, xiàng shì tǎo rén de xǐ huān,
 ràng fù zài àn zhōng kàn nǐ zhōng xīn chì dǎn.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>759</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>